Name: BabyBuddy
Overview:
BabyBuddy is a buddy for babies! Helps caregivers track sleep, feedings, diaper changes, tummy time and more to learn about and predict babys needs without (as much) guess work.

The default user/pass are admin:admin

Full credit to the developers and LSIO for the container. I just wanted to get it out to people who need it, please support their work using the donation link in the template.
